## SwiftSense
A website using MERN stack development, which keep record different stores, amount of products and daily sales of store in different region. Admin can view the daily sales of each store in graphical form and also download the csv file and use it for sales Forecasting. Sales Forecasting is done by prophet algorithm which we trained on different datasets.
